_:Nfd8bc74b80b240fa8d9cbf7543ab2f4b <http://schema.org/description> "UK Research and Innovation (UKRI) is the national funding agency investing in science and research in the UK. Operating across the whole of the UK with a combined budget of more than £6 billion, UKRI brings together the 7 Research Councils, Innovate UK and Research England. UKRI is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Department for Science, Innovation and Technology ." .
